Mae shared "Diamond" on SoundCloud for International Women's Day on March 8, 2016.
It was featured on WXPN that day and has been in rotation since.
Mae toured in support of Benjamin Francis Leftwich, Bobby Long, Ari Hest, and Jay Brannan in 2016 and has emerged at the forefront of the Philadelphia music scene.
Rookie Magazine premiered the title track of Mae's EP, Closer, on October 25, 2016.
Closer is due out November 11, 2016.
